<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Characteristic Species</h4>
	<div class="text"> <i>Festuca</i> <i>brachyphylla</i> is dominant, co-dominant, or characteristically present in the herbaceous and subshrub layers with <i>Antennaria</i> <i>media</i>, <i>Carex</i> <i>phaeocephala</i>, <i>Carex</i> <i>subnigricans</i>, <i>Draba</i> <i>breweri</i>, <i>Eriogonum</i> <i>ovalifolium</i>, <i>Ivesia</i> <i>lycopodioides</i>, <i>Penstemon</i> <i>davidsonii</i> and <i>Poa</i> <i>glauca</i> ssp. <i>rupicola</i>. </div>
</div>

        
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Vegetation Layers</h4>
	<div class="text">  Herbs < 15 cm; cover is open. </div>
</div>

        
