<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fire is typically not important in these open alpine stands. Natural processes affecting stands include shifting snow accumulation, processes involved in patterned ground development, and rock fall.</div>
